24:01.273 --> 24:03.191
Chanel is a very different kind of place.

24:03.275 --> 24:06.319
It's French, it's continental, it's--

24:06.403 --> 24:08.321
Not just another
Jewish department store?

24:08.405 --> 24:09.489
Exactly.

24:09.573 --> 24:11.324
You were right, Roger.

24:11.408 --> 24:13.743
This place really runs on charm .

24:13.828 --> 24:15.495
- This is ridiculous.
- Don .

24:15.579 --> 24:17.747
I'm not gonna let a woman
