27:58.510 --> 28:00.511
Don , I think maybe that's your cue.

28:02.681 --> 28:04.849
Well , uh . . .

28:04.933 --> 28:07.060
I have been , uh . . .

28:08.312 --> 28:10.563
thinking quite a bit about this,

28:10.647 --> 28:12.148
and , uh. . .

28:23.452 --> 28:28.122
I mean, you know I'm a Lucky Strike man
from way back, so. . .

28:35.672 --> 28:36.798
